- Lets you control inbound and outbound traffic
- Think of security group as a virtual firewall
- Applied to all AWS Component including EC2 instance,Elastic load balancer
- Security group are assigned at component level
- On any firewall the more rules it have to process the greater the time
Defaults
- 5 security groups
- each security group have 60 inbound outbound rules
- Single security group can have total 120 rules
- By Default A VPC is limited to 2500 Security groups
- Security groups are Stateful
